# Heaps Demo for Live2D Cubism (HL target)
# ==================================================
# Compile: haxe test\heaps_demo.hxml   (from dev/)
#   or:    haxe heaps_demo.hxml        (from test/)
# Run:     copy_heaps.bat  (copy dependencies)
#          hl bin\heaps\heaps_demo.hl
#
# Required haxelibs: heaps, hlsdl, live2d-haxe, format (auto via heaps)
# Required native: live2d_hl.hdll, Live2DCubismCore.dll, libhl.dll, sdl.hdll (via copy_heaps.bat)

-cp .
-lib heaps
-lib hlsdl
-lib live2d-haxe
-D heaps
-D live2d_haxe
-dce full
-main HeapsDemo
-hl bin/heaps/heaps_demo.hl
